- Dist::Inkt::Role::Release
	- prompts, then uploads to CPAN
	- runs after tests

- Dist::Inkt::Role::HgTag
	- integrates with DIR::Release
	- does: hg tag $VERSION; hg push

- Dist::Inkt::Role::Test::Pod
	- syntax
	- coverage
	- spelling

- Dist::Inkt::Role::Test::Changes
	- check that RDF changelog data covers current version
